    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadOnlyScmRepositoryDto

    public class ScmRepositoryDto
extends TrackerDto
    ScmRepositoryDto is a special tracker for changes in a source code repository like CVS, Subversion, Mercurial or GIT Sub types can define additional attributes, but must store the attributes values in the generic configuration Map of this class, otherwise they wont be persisted.
